WEBVTT

00:00:28.046 --> 00:00:31.008
and discover livestock in his office.

00:00:32.019 --> 00:00:35.183
We thought the whole thing
would last maybe 10 minutes,

00:00:35.207 --> 00:00:39.731
and a few hundred company employees
would log in for the inside joke.

00:00:40.132 --> 00:00:41.395
But what happened?

00:00:41.977 --> 00:00:43.695
Ze kept on getting delayed:

00:00:43.719 --> 00:00:45.205
he went to get a drink,

00:00:45.229 --> 00:00:46.677
he was called to a meeting,

00:00:46.701 --> 00:00:48.444
the meeting ran long,

00:00:48.468 --> 00:00:49.633
he went to the bathroom.

00:00:49.657 --> 00:00:53.877
More and more people
started logging in to watch the goats.

00:00:54.493 --> 00:00:58.506
By the time Ze walked in
more than 30 minutes later,

00:00:58.530 --> 00:01:03.636
90,000 viewers were watching
the livestream.